<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَتَفْصِيل ذَلِكَ فِي مُصْطَلَحِ:</span> <span class="c2">(حَيَوَان ف ٥)</span> <span class="c2">(وَرِفْق ف ١٠)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلِلْعَجْمَاءِ أَحْكَامٌ أُخْرَى كَبَيْعِهَا وَإِجَارَتِهَا وَرَهْنِهَا وَإِعَارَتِهَا وَاقْتِنَائِهَا وَنَحْوِ ذَلِكَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَيُنْظَرُ تَفْصِيل هَذِهِ الأَْحْكَامِ فِي مُصْطَلَحَاتِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عُجْمَة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> أَعْجَمِيّ، وَلُغَة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>